{"tid":594727,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國歌法】二次創作會否違法？　消息人士：有些界線不應踩","createTime":"2018-03-16T05:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T06:22:35.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"981db9da7487a27a7eeb1894197dedd6fc0929c4","tid":594727,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180316/s00001/c467d398936ce1e4b6de5d1aab6a38c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180316%2Fs00001%2Fc467d398936ce1e4b6de5d1aab6a38c8.jpg&h=6403ff76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國歌法將進行本地立法，政府提供的本地立法建議條文內容概要指出，任何人公開及故意篡改國歌歌詞、曲譜，以歪曲、貶損方式奏唱國歌，或以其他方式侮辱國歌，即屬犯罪，一經定罪可判處5萬元罰款及監禁3年。<br />\n<br />\n外界關注二次創作等會否墮入法網，政府消息人士指國歌是國家的象徵、國家的體現，「唔係拎去玩，有些界線不應該踩」，但直言事例是講不清，最重要是尊重國歌，而貶損國歌需要有意圖和用意，強調一般人毋須擔心，「不會咁易誤墮法網」。<br />\n<br />\n政府消息人士又稱，國歌並非流行曲，不可憑個人喜好改變。至於若有人對政治不滿而以國歌表達，消息人士指對政治不滿有很多表達方式，直言即使不喜歡祖國，但亦要接受，「你唔鍾意都好，你都係要跟阿爸姓」。<br />\n<br />\n歌手黎明主唱的《全日愛》、李克勤的《球迷奇遇記》都被指有改編國歌的部分，消息人士形容有關歌曲「有人話似（國歌）、有人話唔似」，強調最重要是意圖。至於《國歌法》會否妨礙創作自由，消息人士相信表達意見與用什麼方式表達是可區分，「若好愛國，可以用其他方式表達，擔心（墮入法網）便無謂走去試」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180316/s00001/1521176431556\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180316%2Fs00001%2F1521176431556&d=700AN3tn0fjhpXEbPZT%2BlWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=60f3be6f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180316%2Fs00001%2F1521176431556&h=99a31eec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180316/s00001/1521176431556</a>"},{"pid":"0b6e3d5621195c8bf8a31b2aa4e4e33e033382ca","tid":594727,"uid":38671,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:23:26.000Z","msg":"所謂個仔老過所謂阿爸<br />\n爸乜撚野爸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42351525c2cab92bc9b6e5f23de7bc4904218f6e","tid":594727,"uid":61398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:29:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d82b681d3e4a9a53ff98f484c6a4172f62480db0","tid":594727,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:30:55.000Z","msg":"on9 都俾到人去改名啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1827a2870fea8721f68f5b8353ab9bb38307a923","tid":594727,"uid":20352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:31:28.000Z","msg":"幫國歌打call 又點計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4beec810436e4d70b15117843ac0ceac0781e66","tid":594727,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:31:38.000Z","msg":"擔心（墮入法網）便無謂走去試」。<br />\n依家係人地唔清楚你條界線，含糊到仆街要求你介定點先係合理，你依家叫人唔敢就唔好做？你咩政府呀白癡<br />\n華人政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f1c370de03779d2cff82457cb1883921d83f4f7","tid":594727,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T05:33:02.000Z","msg":"最高坐三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f9d340af38484d57deea5e70171ee9bcab6c947","tid":594727,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:05:35.000Z","msg":"屌你，老母個臭化閪窿。"},{"pid":"d67124f5c647cdaef21c4d46997fb8346a97c1d1","tid":594727,"uid":21035,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T06:22:35.000Z","msg":"以前要個仔買電飯煲電視接濟你，到有錢就話阿仔如果冇我你餓死咗好耐喇<br />\n<br />\n早幾年又傳染沙士俾個仔<br />\n<br />\n仲同個養母講打斷個仔手手腳腳都要搶返個仔返黎<br />\n<br />\n如果我係個仔我改名做激烈的海膽算撚數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}